                total XRP Ledger network valued at approximately <strong>$80 billion</strong>.
                Unlike Bitcoin or Ethereum, XRP does not rely on proof-of-work mining; the
                ledger uses a <strong>federated consensus mechanism</strong> operated by
                independent validators worldwide.
              </p>

              {/* Table of Contents */}
              <nav className="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8 rounded-lg">
                <h2 className="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-b border-gray-300 pb-2">Contents</h2>
